      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks these are safer. but honestly, do you think it's actually possible to do this without it being seen as \"political\"? like, if i just talk about \"every body,\" some people might still claim i'm following a specific political agenda or DEI trend. do you think there's a \"right\" way to handle this, or is any mention of inclusivity basically just stepping into a political minefield nowadays?",
